channel.title: Comments on: Overheard in Guild Ventrilo

item.title: By: nordee
item.dc:creator: nordee
item.description: I don't think that it's hunter players, per se, are any more stupid than others. I just think it's possible to play a hunter at a high level moderately well without really knowing what you are doing or why.
